cast.overview: A young couple living in a Connecticut suburb during the mid-1950s struggle to come to terms with their personal problems while trying to raise their two children. Based on a novel by Richard Yates.
cast.title: Revolutionary Road

details.biography: Heidi Armbruster is an American actress and playwright based in New York. She holds a Master of Fine Arts in Acting from American Conservatory Theater in San Francisco. Armbruster is a founding member and co-curator of Dorset Theater Festival’s Women Artists Writing.
details.name: Heidi Armbruster
